In the given array if there is a string separated by comma, then replace them with separate string as shown below
  With string
    ip: ["vinoj, arjun", "dixy", "amala"],
    op: ["vinoj", "arjun", "dixy", "amala"]
    
Flatten the given array of objects
  With objects
    ip: [ [{name: "vinoj"}, {name: "dixy"}], {name: "amala"}, {name: "arjun"}]
    op: [ {name: "vinoj"}, {name: "dixy"}, {name: "amala"}, {name: "arjun"}]